# Internationalization & Copy

## Rules
- **No hardcoded user-facing strings**: Use `'key'.tr` in widgets/controllers
- Add translations to [lib/app/translations/app_translations.dart](mdc:lib/app/translations/app_translations.dart)

## Keys & Usage
- **Namespaced keys**: `home.title`, `favourites.empty`, `visits.scheduleCta`
- **Parameters**: `'greeting_name'.trParams({'name': userName})`
- **Keep English complete**: Add other languages incrementally

## Testing
- Switch locale to catch missing keys
- Avoid string concatenation in UI